OL,3,CMan who broke into airport twice in
OL,4,Cone weekend jailed for 25 days
OL,6,FA man has been sentenced to 25 days in
OL,7,Fprison after breaking into Guernsey
OL,8,FAirport twice in one weekend.
OL,10,FOn Friday 20 February, Guernsey's
OL,11,FRoyal Court heard how Russell Payne,
OL,12,F52, trespassed on the airport's
OL,13,Frestricted ground on both Saturday 11
OL,14,Fand Sunday 12 October.
OL,16,FPayne said that he believed the area
OL,17,Fwas an "old school field" on both
OL,18,Fdays, arguing he was going out for a
OL,19,Frun on both occasions.
