OL,3,CMan who broke into airport twice in
OL,4,Cone weekend jailed for 25 days
OL,6,FJudge Marc Davies sentenced Payne
OL,7,Fimmediately after finding him guilty
OL,8,Fof five offences.
OL,10,FPayne was found not guilty of one
OL,11,Fcount of indecent exposure - he had
OL,12,Fpleaded not guilty to all six charges.
OL,14,FThe offender was fined #500 for
OL,15,Fentering a restricted space and given
OL,16,Fa two-month suspended prison sentence
OL,17,Ffor assaulting an emergency worker and
OL,18,Fresisting arrest.
