OL,3,CMan who broke into airport twice in
OL,4,Cone weekend jailed for 25 days
OL,6,FHowever, he chose not to pay the fine
OL,7,Fand ended up going to prison for 25
OL,8,Fdays instead.
OL,10,FOn Saturday 11 October 2025, Payne was
OL,11,Fseen on the wrong side of the fence at
OL,12,F5am.
OL,14,FThis CCTV footage shows him wandering
OL,15,Faround the airport before dawn, coming
OL,16,Fwithin feet of parked planes, before
OL,17,Feventually he was stopped by staff and
OL,18,Farrested for the first time.
