OL,3,CMan who broke into airport twice in
OL,4,Cone weekend jailed for 25 days
OL,6,FThe next day, Payne was arrested
OL,7,Fagain, this time during airport
OL,8,Foperating hours near the runway.
OL,10,FOn this occasion, he was naked from
OL,11,Fthe waist down.
OL,13,FPayne told the court that he suffered
OL,14,Ffrom a skin condition that leaves him
OL,15,Fnumb, and he had a large blue t-shirt
OL,16,Fon, so he didn't realise he wasn't
OL,17,Fwearing shorts.
