OL,3,CMan who broke into airport twice in
OL,4,Cone weekend jailed for 25 days
OL,6,FHowever, without evidence to prove he
OL,7,Fwas exposing himself purposefully to
OL,8,Fupset other people, he was found not
OL,9,Fguilty of this offence.
OL,11,FPayne's recollection of events
OL,12,Fconstantly differed from witness
OL,13,Ftestimony and CCTV footage, including
OL,14,Fcompletely different memories of time
OL,15,Fand place.
