OL,3,CMan who broke into airport twice in
OL,4,Cone weekend jailed for 25 days
OL,6,FRichard Thomasson, Airport Director at
OL,7,FGuernsey Ports, said: "Any incursion
OL,8,Fof the airport is a criminal offence,
OL,9,Fand any member of the public who
OL,10,Fattempts to illegally access the
OL,11,Faerodrome will be liable for
OL,12,Fprosecution, as this case demonstrates.
OL,14,F"Although aerodrome incursions are
OL,15,Fextremely rare, we take such incidents
OL,16,Fvery seriously.
